Package Camp

package Camp
The `Camp` package contains classes and functionalities related to camp management within the Camp Management System.

Key classes and functionalities in this package include:

  • CampInformation: Represents detailed information about a camp, including its name, location, description, dates, etc.
  • CampDate: Manages dates and scheduling for camps, allowing users to specify camp start and end dates.
  • CampParticipantManager: Handles the management of camp attendees and committee members, including registration, slot availability, and participant lists.
  • CampUserManager: Manages user roles within camps, such as participants and organizers, and provides access to camp-related functionalities.
  • CampVisibility: Controls the visibility status of camps, allowing organizers to make camps visible or invisible to users.
  • CampSuggestion: Represents suggestions made by users regarding camps and related activities.

The `Camp` package is central to the system's functionality, providing tools for creating, managing, and interacting with camps and their participants.
